      • getConfidence

        public java.lang.Integer getConfidence()
        Returns:
        A value from 0-100 indicating MaxMind's confidence that the country is correct. This attribute is only available from the Insights end point.

      • getIsoCode

        public java.lang.String getIsoCode()
        Returns:
        The two-character ISO 3166-1 alpha code for the country. This attribute is returned by all end points.
